! Using the ProseMirror Editor

!! Enabling the Editor

To enable ProseMirror as the default editor for wikitext tiddlers, go to ''Control Panel > Editing'' and select "prosemirror" as the editor type, or set the [[EditorTypeMappings|$:/config/EditorTypeMappings/text/vnd.tiddlywiki]] tiddler to `prosemirror`.

!! Text Formatting

Use toolbar buttons or keyboard shortcuts:

|!Format |!WikiText |!Shortcut |
|Bold |`''text''` |Ctrl/Cmd+B |
|Italic |`//text//` |Ctrl/Cmd+I |
|Underline |`__text__` |Ctrl/Cmd+U |
|Strikethrough |`~~text~~` | |
|Inline code |<code>``text``</code> |Ctrl/Cmd+` |
|Superscript |`^^text^^` | |
|Subscript |`,,text,,` | |

!! Block Types

Use the ''Type'' dropdown in the toolbar, or press `/` to open the slash menu:

* Heading 1–6 (`!` to `!!!!!!`)
* Blockquote (`>` or `<<<`)
* Code block (triple backtick ` ``` `)
* Horizontal rule (`---`)
* Ordered, unordered, and task lists

!! Links

Click the link icon in the toolbar or use `[[` to start a link. Wiki links navigate within TiddlyWiki; external links open in a new tab.

!! Tables

Insert via the slash menu or toolbar ''Insert > Table''. Tables are 3×3 by default with a header row.

!! Widget Blocks

Macro/widget syntax like `<<macroName "param">>` is automatically detected and rendered as a visual block. Click the block to edit its source.

!! Find & Replace

Press `Ctrl/Cmd+F` to open find, `Ctrl/Cmd+H` to open find & replace.

!! Source Panel

Click the source toggle button in the toolbar to view/edit the raw WikiText side by side.
